revents uppercase intent lookup failures\\n\\nValidation Required:\\n- Confirm lowercase normalization works correctly\\n- Verify all intent categories are accessible\\n- Check fallback to "chat" intent works as expected\', \'key_snippets\': \'\', \'success\': True, \'reason\': None, \'work_log\': \'## 2026-05-13T02:47:36.577810\\n\\nExecuted shell command: cat router.py\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:47:39.703407\\n\\nExecuted shell command: python3 -m pytest tests/test_router_intent_lookup.py -v\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:47:44.882185\\n\\nStored research note #2.\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:47:52.731343\\n\\nExecuted shell command: python3 -m py_compile router.py\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:47:55.299510\\n\\nExecuted shell command: sed -i \\\'s/intent = classification.get("intent", "chat")/intent = classification.get("intent", "chat").lower()/\\\' router.py\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:47:58.307756\\n\\nExecuted shell command: python3 -m pytest tests/test_router_intent_lookup.py -v\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:49:02.568193\\n\\nStored research note #3.\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:49:12.491652\\n\\nStored research note #4.\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:49:13.438257\\n\\nExecuted shell command: python3 -m pytest tests/test_router_intent_lookup.py -v\\n\\n## 2026-05-13T02:49:15.579905\\n\\nExecuted shell command: python3 -m py_compile router.py\'}</last result>', 'role': 'user'}, {'content': 'Your tool call caused an error: Invalid tool call format and LLM extraction is disabled.\\n\\nPlease correct your tool call and try again.', 'role': 'user'}, {'content': 'Your tool call caused an error: Invalid tool call format and LLM extraction is disabled.\\n\\nPlease correct your tool call and try again.', 'role': 'user'}, {'content': '\\n<last result>Your tool call caused an error: Invalid tool call format and LLM extraction is disabled.\\n\\nPlease correct your tool call and try again.</last result>', 'role': 'user'}], 'model': 'anthropic/claude-3.5-haiku', 'stream': False, 'temperature': 0.7}}
