## Modify router.py to Normalize Intent Case

### Task Specification
- Modify the `classify_intent()` function in router.py
- Change intent retrieval to use `.lower()` method
- Ensure lowercase normalization of intent before lookup
- Preserve existing fallback to "chat" intent

### Specific Implementation Details
- Locate the line: `intent = classification.get("intent", "chat")`
- Replace with: `intent = classification.get("intent", "chat").lower()`
- Verify this change maintains existing function logic
- Ensure no other modifications to the function or file

### Validation Criteria
- All tests in test_router_intent_lookup.py must pass
- Py_compile check for router.py must succeed
- No changes to other files in the project

